  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of the Fixed Dose Combination of Glimepiride+Metformin in Type 2 Diabetic Patients Inadequately Controlled</brief_title>
  <acronym>LEGEND</acronym>
  <official_title>A Multinational, Open Label, Non Comparative, 24-week Study to Evaluate the Blood Glucose Lowering Efficacy and Safety of a Fixed Dose Combination of Glimepiride and Metformin in Patients With Inadequately Controlled Type 2 Diabetes</official_title>
  <sponsors>
